<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email - Astral Turf</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header .logo {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555555;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .link-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .link-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666666;
    }
    .link-box a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .expiry-notice {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .expiry-notice p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #856404;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">⚽</div>
      <h1>Astral Turf</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, {{userName}}!</h2>
      
      <p>Thank you for registering with Astral Turf. We're excited to have you join our community of football enthusiasts!</p>
      
      <p>To complete your registration and start using your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
      
      <center>
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
      </center>
      
      <div class="link-box">
        <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}">{{verificationUrl}}</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="expiry-notice">
        <p><strong>⏰ This link expires in 24 hours.</strong></p>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you didn't create an account with Astral Turf, please ignore this email and the account will not be activated.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Astral Turf</strong></p>
      <p>Building the future of football management</p>
      <p>© 2025 Astral Turf. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
